@startuml
title Product Checkout with Sandbox

actor Customer
participant Frontend
participant Backend
database DB
participant Sandbox

Customer -> Frontend: View product
Frontend -> Backend: GET /products/current
Backend -> DB: Fetch active product
DB --> Backend: Product + stock
Backend --> Frontend: Product + stock
Frontend --> Customer: Display product

Customer -> Frontend: Enter card and delivery details
Frontend -> Backend: GET /checkout/config
Backend -> Sandbox: Get acceptance tokens
Sandbox --> Backend: Tokens + legal info
Backend --> Frontend: publicKey + acceptance tokens

Frontend -> Sandbox: Tokenize card
Sandbox --> Frontend: paymentMethodToken

Customer -> Frontend: Confirm purchase
Frontend -> Backend: POST /transactions\n(customer, delivery, productId)
Backend -> DB: Validate product and stock
DB --> Backend: Product available
Backend -> DB: Create Customer, Delivery,\nTransaction(PENDING)
DB --> Backend: transactionId
Backend --> Frontend: transactionId + summary

Frontend -> Backend: POST /transactions/:id/process-payment\n(paymentMethodToken, acceptanceToken, customerEmail)
Backend -> DB: Reload transaction and product
DB --> Backend: Transaction(PENDING) + stock

Backend -> Sandbox: Create payment transaction
Sandbox --> Backend: Payment result

alt Payment approved
  Backend -> DB: Update Transaction(APPROVED)
  Backend -> DB: Decrease stock by 1
  DB --> Backend: OK
  Backend --> Frontend: status=APPROVED
  Frontend --> Customer: Show success
else Payment declined
  Backend -> DB: Update Transaction(DECLINED)
  DB --> Backend: OK
  Backend --> Frontend: status=DECLINED
  Frontend --> Customer: Show decline
else Technical error
  Backend -> DB: Update Transaction(ERROR)
  DB --> Backend: OK
  Backend --> Frontend: status=ERROR
  Frontend --> Customer: Show error
end

Frontend -> Backend: GET /transactions/:id
Backend -> DB: Fetch final status
DB --> Backend: Status + summary
Backend --> Frontend: Final status

Frontend -> Backend: GET /products/current
Backend -> DB: Fetch updated product
DB --> Backend: Product + updated stock
Backend --> Frontend: Updated product
Frontend --> Customer: Display updated product

@enduml